thread.title_full: Oak Park Home & Hardware reviewed by David Dorn

author: David Dorn
title: David Dorn
text: I looked long and hard before I found exactly what I was looking for with these Mission Style Closet Knobs. They are of excellent quality, and arrived in just under two weeks, NOT the four to six weeks that I was lead to believe. They are the finishing touch to my remodeling project..
